comments:
Abolished 30.9.1894 to become the separate parishes of Frindsbury 
    Intra and Frindsbury Extra. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (b).

Created 30.9.1894 from the part of the parish of Frindsbury in 
    Rochester Municipal Borough. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 30.9.1894 from the rural part of the parish of Frindsbury. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).

Abolished 30.9.1894 to become the separate parishes of Strood 
    Intra and Strood Extra. See also Table 2, note (a).

Created 30.9.1894 from the part of the parish of Strood in Rochester 
    Municipal Borough. See also Table 2, note (c).

Created 30.9.1894 from the rural part of the parish of Strood. 
    See also Table 2, note (c).
